com.mousebird.maply

Class VectorStyleSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.VectorStyleSettings

  • public class VectorStyleSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    Settings that control how vector tiles look in relation to their styles. These are set based on the sort of device we're on, particularly retina vs. non-retina. They can be manipulated directly as well for your needs. This is the object backing the ObjC and Android versions.
